He will still miss the remainder of this campaign but fears that he may also be absent for the beginning of next season have been dispelled.

The striker will now rest with his family following the operation but a decision is yet be taken as to whether he will return to Stoke to continue his period of recuperation or if he will remain in Catalonia and use Barcelona's facilities.

 

